This year, Loeries share three years worth of data – this ensures that results are not viewed monadically, but instead, present a record of how companies and individuals have performed over a defined period of time.The Official Rankings is more than just informative – it is a powerful business tool to help the brand communication industry in building the best partnerships between the brands, agencies, production companies, organisations and individuals who continue to demonstrate creative excellence in the work that they do.The Official Rankings is a powerful tool in identifying:Brands that embrace creative excellence as part of their strategy to win the hearts and minds of consumers.Agencies that are able to develop the strongest creative products in the region.Production Companies that bring the creative product to life with a true spirit of excellence.Organisations that ensure that creative excellence is an intrinsic part of the work that they output.Individuals who are able to generate creative excellence through their craft and ultimately influence the creative landscape.Ranking by Brand - Africa and Middle EastRanking2021202020191CHICKEN LICKENCHICKEN LICKENCHICKEN LICKEN2NISSAN BBC STUDIOSCITY LODGE HOTEL GROUP3MASSDISCOUNTERSMASTERCARDPHILIPS & THE NELSON MANDELA FOUNDATION4ADIDASNEDBANKNANDO’S5CONVERSEAN-NAHAR NEWSPAPERAB INBEV6SANLAMFIRST FOR WOMENSANLAM7UAE GOVERNMENT MEDIA OFFICENOVOMED ALLERGY CLINICTHEATRE HOURS8KFCIKEATHE COCA-COLA COMPANY9V&A WATERFRONTHYPE MAGAZINE & TEARS FOUNDATIONMTN9SUPERSPORT & SA RUGBYKFCIKEA11SHELFLIFEAPSARA PEARL GROUP28 TOO MANY12KREEPY KRAULYDSTVSAINT13POWAAB INBEVBBL SECURITY PRODUCTS14MINIHEAD & SHOULDERSKLEINE RIJKE15NEDBANKFIFTYFIFTY LEBANONWASTE MANAGEMENT COALITION16MTNREDEMPTION RUMSTANDARD BANK17RISCURA HOLDINGSETISALATOKAVANGO DIAMOND COMPANY18THE CONSTITUTION HILL TRUSTLOTO LIBANAISINVESTEC19ARRIVE ALIVETOPS AT SPARTIGER BRANDS20LEGOEMIRATES NBDEDGARS21GREG TRUENPOWAJET22KELLOGG'SBOSETURKCELL23SALVATION ARMYCANSA